"Settings
set nu
set relativenumber
set scrolloff=5
set incsearch
set ic

"Plugin
set surround
set easymotion
set NERDTree
set easymotion

"Mark space as a leader key
let mapleader=" "

"Make sure that the space doesn't have any mapping henceforth
nnoremap <SPACE> <Nop>

"Custom key mapping
map <leader>o <Action>(GotoFile)
map <leader>f <Action>(Find)
map <leader>F <Action>(FindInPath)
map <leader>c <Action>($Copy)<Esc>
map <leader>p <Action>($Paste)
map <leader>s <Action>(SaveAll)
nmap <leader>- <action>(SplitHorizontally)
nmap <leader>/ <action>(SplitVertically)
nnoremap <leader>t :action ActivateTerminalToolWindow<CR>
nmap U <action>($Redo)

"NERDTree
nmap <leader>n :NERDTreeFocus<CR>
nmap <leader>nc :NERDTreeFind<CR>

"Navigate between tabs
map ml <Action>(NextSplitter)
nmap mh <Action>(PrevSplitter)
nmap mm :action MoveEditorToOppositeTabGroup<CR>

"Change Tabs
nnoremap <s-TAB> :action PreviousTab<CR>
nnoremap <TAB> :action NextTab<CR>

"Quiting actions
nmap <leader>x <Action>(CloseEditor)
nmap <leader>X <Action>(CloseAllEditorsButActive)
nmap <leader>qa <Action>(CloseAllEditors)

"Motion commands
nmap gf <action>(Forward)
nmap gb <action>(Back)
nmap gd <action>(GotoDeclaration)
nnoremap gi :action GotoImplementation<CR>
nnoremap ge :action GotoNextError<CR>
nnoremap gE :action GotoPreviousError<CR>
nnoremap gt :action GotoTest<CR>
nnoremap <leader>u :action FindUsages<CR>

nmap <A-u> <Action>(Vcs.RollbackChangedLines)

"Current file commands
nmap <leader>r <action>(RenameFile)
nmap <leader>e <action>(RenameElement)
nmap s <Action>(AceAction)
